{"tid":1648791,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今日尖沙咀遊行有53.7萬人","createTime":"2019-10-12T11:11:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T13:32:45.000Z","uid":44751,"like":328,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"5455d1c5b188266d3b41acc1c397f2999113c8a6","tid":1648791,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rczuMQW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrczuMQW.png&h=809dc960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/252483398206116/posts/2448850395236061?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F252483398206116%2Fposts%2F2448850395236061%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=Au6C6jYmoXJsWFOyr%2BboKKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=f99747a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/252483398206116/posts/2448850395236061?sfns=mo</a><br />\n//10.12 53.7萬人<br />\n今次集會係民間搞嘅， 但係我覺得需要有人去點人數，報導是次遊行嘅正確數字出嚟，俾世界知道香港人幾齊心， 所以膽粗粗做咗一個統計。<br />\n<br />\n根據統計今日尖沙咀大遊行人數，約53.7萬人參與， 是九龍歷來最多人參與嘅遊行。<br />\n<br />\n今次計法，係計算路面面積以及人口密度作嘅粗略推算。<br />\n因為經驗尚淺，係遊行人數在四方八面不斷增加， 喺點算方面我哋團隊遇到一定嘅困難。<br />\n<br />\n當中有唔少道路有漏網之魚， 但經過粗略估計， 雖然係星期六，但今日尖沙咀大遊行， 截至目前為止大約有53.7萬人參與。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔知呢個數字報大定報細左 但眼見係好撚多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該大家唔好再講咩運動完左 我深信好多人根本心中嘅火根本冇熄過 尋日輕輕吹雞都有咁多人 大家自己友咪撚再嘈<br />\n其實休整期唔係冇試過 只係今次有好多大事發生都休整不合邏輯 先好似搞到大家放棄左 再加上有人鳩搞活動同亂開post <br />\n<br />\n只有大家早少少決定活動 係三日前做好文宣<br />\n和理非該出就出 前線可留在18區開花 相信呢場運動有排玩 最近美國人先開始憎到中國人仆街 希望大家唔好內鬥 做好國際文宣 <br />\n<br />\n最後 大家可以支持下鄭敬基<br />\n天滅中共 驅除共匪 <br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n不要忘記我們失去嘅戰友"},{"pid":"d14207e1117afb52975dfb31ba0aefec1ca4cd19","tid":1648791,"uid":44751,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:11:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9063d2cf1a7d42ce839d42dfe1e9cd372eb0ce57","tid":1648791,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:11:35.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"0961ddeab9de262d3f7650dfa1dbe0621150959b","tid":1648791,"uid":54228,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:12:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x4BH6OL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx4BH6OL.jpg&h=e16fa6dc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2fec163b2b586187e2f54156ade6b18a5563aa0","tid":1648791,"uid":294,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"真假都好<br />\n點都要出到個數字<br />\n當然真係最好<br />\n<br />\n929咁無人報數，無左個好大意義"},{"pid":"ce0891fb68768002fcc23f79963c0ccaa463dd71","tid":1648791,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3015fb9dbbd606deaeb87226e7096dc089320db2","tid":1648791,"uid":60815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267469bbe9607e91e8776eb9b76f7f6a27b41b47","tid":1648791,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"dc9f8790025104a92ed675161d0dc18aa8d0038c","tid":1648791,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:15:17.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"a7442eb83246d9f0e234ee3882abb91736bb7b3a","tid":1648791,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:15:33.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"d4c500dc90672f9ed5074319f4490a00407d0d46","tid":1648791,"uid":32906,"like":13,"dislike":9,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T11:15:41.000Z","msg":"老實講吹大左好多"},{"pid":"f0f6fc088eae7b736c1a14db8ff13dc1a627d90a","tid":1648791,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB